Content: About Us:NLWe are a small  clan hoping to grow. We have a Legends Team_ Pro Team_ and a Casual Team. We want to be able to pull out the best of your potential and become better but also be able to communicate with new people!NLNLContent Creators:NLWe are looking for content creators for YouTube_ and Twitch to help us grow through social media and for them to make montages for the team members etc!NL—————————————————-NLGFX Designers:NLLooking for GFX Designers to create logos_ banners_ templates for the clan and team members!NL—————————————————NLTry-out staff:NLWe are looking for active people that are able to recruit and try them out for the clan daily!NL—————————————————NLTrainers:NLWe are now looking for people who qualify for professional or legends team to help train up people that would like to become better at the game!NL—————————————————NLSome things you should keep in mind:NLYou must have a mic_NLDon't be toxic_NLDo not disrespect anyone in the clan.NLNLHave Fun! :)NLNL============================NLYou will be going through tryouts to see what team you qualify for.NLNL------------------------------------------------------NL--The legends--NL13+ of age_NL300+ wins_NLGreat Builder_NLMust have a mic_NLGood call outs_NLHelp with tryouts (optional)NLNL------------------------------------------------------NL--Pro Team--NL125+ wins_NLGood builder_NLMust have a mic_NLDecent call outs.NLNL------------------------------------------------------NL--Casual Team--NL60+ Wins_NL0.75kd_NLMust have a mic.NLNL------------------------------------------------------NLNLIf you would like to join_ send me a DM to be invited!

EL1T3 CLAN    ➢ General InfoNLWe are an all around clan_ and are very versatile with our selection of recruits.NLNL➢ Pro Players (Competitive)NLIn order to compete in events_ we need the best of the best to play for our team.NLNL➢ Snipers (Casual)NLWe need people who can hit consistent clips to give to our editors for montages.NLNL➢ GFX and EditorsNL Editors and GFX designers are needed to make thumbnails_ montages_ edits and logos for the team.(PAID)NLNL➢ Content CreatorsNLWe are in need of players who will be able to make content for the official EL1T3 Clan channel.NLNL➢ SponsorshipsNLWe are currently supported by Fatal Grips. Use Code FEAREL1T3 to save 10%!NLNLOther Requirements:NL➟ You must be able to make a #EL1T3 video.NL➟ You must be at least 13 years of age. NL➟ You must be active (In Discord & in game)NL➟ You must be able to use the in game VC AND Discord VCNL➟ You must speak fluent English.NL➟ You must be loyal to the clan.NL➟ You have to be able to learn from your mistakes and your clips.NL➟ There is absolutely no being in other clans at the same time.NLNLDM <@411676789358854145> for more information!
